name: EDMONTON PLANE SPOTTING! Winter Aviation at Edmonton International Airport (4K)
description:
Back at the start of January, I spent a few days in Alberta's capital and filmed some winter plane spotting action with @MarkBrandonAviation!

As the 5th busiest airport in the country (by passengers), Edmonton has a pretty decent amount of traffic, with service from almost every major Canadian airline, and now Porter as well (as of February 14th).

Enjoy this snowy plane spotting at YEG!
